(lp15
VWe would like to thank all scientists and crew from the Autonomous
p16
aVEcological Surveys of the Abyss (AESA) 2012 cruise, Alice Horton for
p17
aVassistance with the experiment at sea, Ben Boorman for design and
p18
aVbuilding of apparatus and Maureen Procee and Gillian Martin for
p19
aVtechnical assistance and tuition in the laboratory. This work was
p20
aVcarried out as part of the SERPENT project www.serpentproject.com. DJM
p21
